title: Dash: Racing, Karting, Driving Music
description: This music pack contains 11 loopable tracks and over 49 minutes of high-energy music designed for racing games, karting games, combat games, and everything in-between.
longDescription:
This music pack contains 11 loopable tracks and over 49 minutes* of high-energy music designed for racing games, karting games, combat games, and everything in-between. These high-energy, positive, feel-good tracks make this pack perfect for energetic, fun games across many videogame genres.


* total duration includes full length tracks + the loopable versions of the tracks, see more detailed breakdown in the "technical information" section.


Soundcloud Preview


An additional 11 full-length versions of the loopable tracks are included. The full-length versions are not automatically loopable, but they feature additional sections not present in the loopable versions.
